                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">'policeman, G</hi> 122). On the afternoon of 12th Feb. I was at home, and saw the prisoner and two others loitering about—the prisoner took this chest—I was lame but I opened the window and sprung my rattle, and called "Stop thief!"—he dropped it and ran away.</p>
